title: A proclamacion, set furth by the Kynges Maiestie with the assent of his dearest vncle, Edward Duke of Somerset, gouernor of his moste royall persone and of his realmes dominions and subiectes protector, and others of his highnes moste honorable priute counsayl, concernyng the prolongacion of the former proclamacion made for the callyng in of testons.
author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1547-1553 : Edward VI)
